{
  "stem": "15540.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My name is Mette Shayne, M-E-T-T-E S-H-A-Y-N-E.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hannover.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "H-A-N-N-O-V-E-R.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was born October 9, 1934.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "61.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was born in Copenhagen, Denmark.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The, the first known in my family to come to Denmark came in 1683, was one of the first Jews that came to Denmark and was allowed to, to settle and, and work in Denmark.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and all of my family seemed to have a, a, a genealogy that goes back that far.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They came from Germany.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That time--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This person settled in Copenhagen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think some came up through Jutland, and so they-- but they eventually ended up in Copenhagen.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And by far, most of the Jews in Denmark live in Copenhagen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there aren't so many.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You mean way back?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think they were merchants, and later on became academicians as well.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember so much before, before the war, except some family life in general.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a close family, the, the extended family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I have one brother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But, so the first things that I remember is from going to school and living in the house that we lived in was built when I was born.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it had affectionate relation to the-- and then the first I remember as far as the war was concerned was in April 9, 1940, when the German, Germans invaded Denmark.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my, my-- in the house was my brother and my, and my parents.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had, at that time, one had maids, and we had two maids living with us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had a maid that took me to school on a bicycle in the morning.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and I'm still in contact with her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was in the suburb, but just, just on the border of Copenhagen.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
